battlecode.common

Class BulletInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • battlecode.common.BulletInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BodyInfo

    public class BulletInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements BodyInfo
    Struct that stores basic information that was 'sensed' of a Bullet. This info is ephemeral and there is no guarantee any of it will remain the same between rounds.
